    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>List is an Interface . You cant use List to initialize it.</p>\n\n<pre><code>  List&lt;String&gt; supplierNames = new ArrayList&lt;String&gt;();\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>These are the some of List impelemented classes,</p>\n\n<pre><code>ArrayList, LinkedList, Vector\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>You could use any of this as per your requirement. These each classes have its own features.</p>\n"
  }, {
    "owner" : {
      "account_id" : 1036092,
      "reputation" : 8902,
      "user_id" : 1043352,
      "user_type" : "registered",
      "accept_rate" : 81,
      "profile_image" : "https://www.gravatar.com/avatar/f336066e4f8700aa439943ee4f5ffbd9?s=256&d=identicon&r=PG",
      "display_name" : "Jakub Zaverka",
      "link" : "https://stackoverflow.com/users/1043352/jakub-zaverka"
