    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>We created <a href=\"https://github.com/thedocs-io/soyuz-to\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">soyuz-to</a> to simplify 1 problem: how to convert <code>X</code> to <code>Y</code> (e.g. <code>String</code> to <code>Integer</code>). Constructing of an object is also kind of conversion so it has a simple function to construct <code>Map</code>, <code>List</code>, <code>Set</code>: </p>\n\n<pre class=\"lang-java prettyprint-override\"><code>import io.thedocs.soyuz.to;\n\nList&lt;String&gt; names = to.list(\"John\", \"Fedor\");\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>Please check it - it has a lot of other useful features</p>\n"
  }, {
