    "is_accepted" : false,
    "score" : 3,
    "last_activity_date" : 1621618749,
    "creation_date" : 1621618749,
    "answer_id" : 67641562,
    "question_id" : 13395114,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>Instead of :</p>\n<pre><code>List&lt;String&gt; supplierNames = new List&lt;String&gt;();\n</code></pre>\n<p>Write this if you are using latest JDK:</p>\n<pre><code> List&lt;String&gt; supplierNames = new ArrayList&lt;&gt;();\n</code></pre>\n<p>It's the correct way of initializing a List.</p>\n"
